Package com.niklasarndt.healthchecksio Description

Welcome to the healthchecks-io Documentation!

The basic classes of the project are located here:

  • Healthchecks - Contains the functions to retrieve a manager/client object
  • HealthchecksClient - Contains all functionality of the Pinging API
  • HealthchecksManager - Contains all functionality of the Management API
  • HealthchecksInfo - Contains information such as library version and build timestamp

The implementation classes are located in this package as well, but not relevant for the documentation.

Since:
1.0.0
